,
D


{\displaystyle D_{x},D_{y},D}

分別是如下三個行列式：




D
=

|





a

1





b

1







a

2





b

2






|



{\displaystyle D=\left|{\begin{matrix}a_{1}&b_{1}\\a_{2}&b_{2}\end{matrix}}\right|}

, 




D

x


=

|





c

1





